name: I Read The News Today
description:
Brand New Design from Art Feministe and Daisy Chain!

Art Feministe brings us this unique design with a high brow critique of today's media.

Grab it today in a slim fit style, dress it with an oversize cardigan or cut to complete the look and wear on it's own.

Unisex, 100% Cotton, Machine Washable.

name: Bright Sky Night
description:
Jamille Graves and Daisy Chain join forces to turn a Yorkshire Garden into an extra terrestrial fashion phenom.

This richly coloured stellar tee is great worn as a statement in a plain outfit or layered up to create a unique look.

Unisex. 100% Cotton. Machine Washable.

name: Alice In Chains
description:
Alice follows in the footsteps of Frank Sinatra, Hugh Grant and Lindsay Lohan as the law finally catch up with her.

The unique Alice mugshot is a defining piece in the Daisy Chain collection, Alice's eyes pierce through you, failing to hide her femininity with her striking red lips as she bares her prison placard.

Worn baggy or slim with skinny jeans or leggings, looks amazing on either boys or girls and will be a staple of your wardrobe for the foreseeable future.

Get it now.

Unisex. 100% Cotton. Machine Washable. Beautiful.

name: American Polaroid Dream
description:
Polaroid is not for yesterday.

Nostalgic look at Palm Springs in the time it first made its name.

Full length graphic tee worn lazily over jeans or cut up for a night out with the ladies.

Unisex, 100% Cotton, Machine Washable, 100% Loveable, iron on reverse. Get it. xx

name: The Rest Of The Chain
description: You thought it was over? There is much more to Daisy Chain's repertoire not shown here; with the finest vintage, unique graphic jumpers, beautiful jewellery, Daisy Chain love to dress you to standout in a unique and undeniably fresh way. Check us out at a fair near you, but in the mean time... Disorderly Conduct (Grey Mugshot) - Straight from jail, Alice watch out!; Beach Life (White) - Take Summer all through Autumn/Winter in this eye catching graphic; 3 As A Bird (White) - Fly free in either vest or tee in this three image special designed by Daisy Chain's own Maddie Knight; Polaroid Sky (White Vest) - Oversized ladies vest bringing the outside-in, an offshoot of the runaway success '3 As A Bird'. e-mail daisy_chain_clothing@live.com or for more information go to www.facebook.com/daisychainclothing Thanks for coming and we'll see you soon, Love Daisy Chain xx
